<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">双向隔离标签</span></strong> <strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;bdi&gt;</span></strong></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;bdi&gt;</span></span>
        <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">标签告诉浏览器的双向算法将其包含的文本与周围的文本隔离，当网站动态插入一些文本且不知道所插入文本的方向性时，此功能特别有用。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>

<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">内容模板</span></strong>
        <strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;template&gt;</span></strong></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;template&gt;</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）元素是一种用于保存客户端内容机制，该内容在加载页面时不会呈现，但随后可以</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> (</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">原文为</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> may be)
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在运行时使用</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> JavaScript
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">实例化。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">将模板视为一个可存储在文档中以便后续使用的内容片段。虽然解析器在加载页面时确实会处理</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> &lt;template&gt;
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">元素的内容，但这样做只是为了确保这些内容有效；但元素内容不会被渲染。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
